Turn an Item into a Bucket
----field----
field: {E4671EDD-3EB2-4634-A944-B5D86397D111}
name: Tip Text
key: tip text
content-length: 375

Any item can be turned into a bucket. It does not only have to be a folder or a reserved item. Good candidates for buckets are:
Items that contain more than 40 children or sibling items.
Items that contain children that are very heavily nested.
Items that contain items that are very complex and have lots of fields.
Items that should not have a parent to child relationship.
